
<div style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(150,0,0,0.1),rgba(150,0,0,0.1)), url(https://res.cloudinary.com/dzjwppn5k/image/upload/v1668649308/green-ambient-bg_coebud.jpg);width: 100vw; height: 100vh; background-size: fill; opacity: 0.5">
